# UI Global Style System Rules

IMPORTANT: Minimize the use of AI generated comments, instead use clearly named variables and functions.

## Color System
- **Color Space**: Use OKLCH color format for all colors (e.g., `oklch(0.55 0.18 160)`)
- **CSS Variables**: Always use CSS variables from `app/globals.css` instead of hardcoded colors
- **Color Tokens**:
  - `bg-background` / `text-foreground` - Main background and text
  - `bg-primary` / `text-primary-foreground` - Primary actions
  - `bg-secondary` / `text-secondary-foreground` - Secondary elements
  - `bg-accent` / `text-accent-foreground` - Accent color (green: oklch(0.55 0.18 160))
  - `bg-muted` / `text-muted-foreground` - Muted/secondary text
  - `border-border` - Border color
  - `bg-destructive` / `text-destructive-foreground` - Error/destructive actions

