## Typography
- **Font Family**: 
  - Sans-serif: `font-sans` (Inter font family)
  - Monospace: `font-mono` (Geist Mono)
- **Font Sizes**: Use Tailwind text scale (text-sm, text-base, text-lg, text-xl, text-2xl, text-3xl, text-4xl, text-5xl, text-6xl, text-7xl)
- **Font Weights**: Use `font-medium`, `font-semibold`, `font-bold` as needed
- **Line Height**: Use `leading-relaxed` for body text, `tracking-tight` for headings
- **Text Utilities**: 
  - `text-balance` for headings
  - `text-pretty` for paragraphs
  - `gradient-text` for gradient text effects

## Spacing & Padding
- **Container Padding**: 
  - Horizontal: `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8` (standard container padding)
  - Max width containers: `max-w-7xl mx-auto`
- **Section Padding**: 
  - Vertical: `py-28 sm:py-36` (standard section spacing)
  - Use `pt-28 sm:pt-36 lg:pt-44` for hero sections
- **Component Padding**:
  - Buttons: `px-4 py-2` (default), `px-8` (large buttons), `px-6` (lg size)
  - Cards: `p-8` (standard card padding)
  - Small elements: `px-3 py-1.5` or `px-4 py-2`
- **Gap Spacing**: Use `gap-2`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`, `gap-8` for flex/grid layouts
- **Margin**: Use `mt-4`, `mt-8`, `mt-10`, `mt-16` for vertical spacing between elements

## Border Radius
- **Base Radius**: `--radius: 0.75rem` (12px)
- **Radius Variants**:
  - `rounded-sm` - Small (calc(var(--radius) - 4px))
  - `rounded-md` - Medium (calc(var(--radius) - 2px))
  - `rounded-lg` - Large (var(--radius))
  - `rounded-xl` - Extra large (calc(var(--radius) + 4px))
  - `rounded-2xl` - For cards and large containers
  - `rounded-full` - For pills and circular elements

## Shadows
- **Shadow Scale**:
  - `shadow-xs` - Subtle shadow
  - `shadow-sm` - Small shadow
  - `shadow-md` - Medium shadow
  - `shadow-lg` - Large shadow
  - `shadow-xl` - Extra large shadow
- **Accent Shadows**: Use `shadow-accent/20` or `shadow-accent/30` for colored shadows
- **Hover Shadows**: Enhance on hover: `hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/30`

## Borders
- **Border Width**: `border` (1px) or `border-b` for bottom borders
- **Border Color**: Use `border-border` or `border-accent/30` for colored borders
- **Border Style**: `border-border/40` for semi-transparent borders

## Backgrounds
- **Glass Morphism**: 
  - `bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl` or `bg-white/60` with `backdrop-blur-xl`
  - Use `supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-white/60` for progressive enhancement
- **Gradients**:
  - Background gradients: `bg-gradient-to-b from-[color] via-[color] to-[color]`
  - Text gradients: Use `.gradient-text` utility class
- **Overlays**: Use `bg-accent/10`, `bg-accent/15`, `bg-accent/5` for subtle colored backgrounds

## Animations
- **Custom Animations** (from globals.css):
  - `animate-gradient` - Gradient shift animation (8s)
  - `animate-glow-pulse` - Glow pulse effect (4s)
  - `animate-float` - Float animation (6s)
  - `animate-marquee` - Marquee scroll (30s)
  - `animate-pulse-ring` - Pulsing ring (2s)
- **Framer Motion**: Use for interactive animations
  - `whileHover={{ scale: 1.02 }}` for hover scale
  - `whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}` for tap feedback
  - `transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}` for smooth transitions
- **Transitions**: Always use `transition-all duration-300` for smooth state changes

## Buttons
- **Base Styles**: Use `Button` component from `@/components/ui/button`
- **Variants**:
  - `default` - Primary button with `bg-primary`
  - `accent` - Use `bg-accent text-accent-foreground hover:bg-accent/90`
  - `outline` - Border with transparent background
  - `secondary` - Secondary background
  - `ghost` - Transparent with hover state
- **Sizes**: `sm`, `default`, `lg`
- **Button Enhancements**:
  - Add `shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/30` for accent buttons
  - Use `px-8` for large call-to-action buttons

## Layout Patterns
- **Container Structure**:
  ```tsx
  <section className="relative py-28 sm:py-36">
    <div className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      {/* Content */}
    </div>
  </section>
  ```
- **Centered Content**: `mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center` for centered text blocks
- **Grid Layouts**: Use `grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3` for responsive grids
- **Flex Layouts**: Use `flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row`

## Z-Index Scale
- **Layers**:
  - `z-10` - Overlay elements
  - `z-50` - Sticky headers/navigation
  - `-z-10` - Background elements

## Responsive Breakpoints
- **Mobile First**: Always design mobile-first
- **Breakpoints**:
  - `sm:` - 640px and up
  - `md:` - 768px and up
  - `lg:` - 1024px and up
  - `xl:` - 1280px and up

## Component Patterns
- **Sections**: Always wrap in `<section>` with proper padding
- **Headings**: Use semantic heading tags (h1-h6) with appropriate sizes
- **Text Hierarchy**: 
  - Headings: `text-foreground`
  - Body: `text-muted-foreground` or `text-foreground/80`
  - Labels: `text-muted-foreground`
- **Interactive Elements**: Always include hover and focus states
- **Accessibility**: Use proper ARIA labels, semantic HTML, and keyboard navigation

## Code Style
- **Class Order**: Group classes logically: layout → spacing → typography → colors → effects
- **Conditional Classes**: Use `cn()` utility from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes
- **Component Structure**: Use TypeScript, proper prop types, and React best practices
- Ensure all components are reusable and follow the existing design patterns.
- Ensure all components are responsive and accessible.
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling, adhering to the defined color palette.

